{"tid":2495992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府豪花近億游說僅換1票反對《人權法案》","createTime":"2021-04-19T13:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T13:54:42.000Z","uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"019e753e5da94a25fd7dc00efeb2c40ff0ad6eea","tid":2495992,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=504a6dc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE%2F&h=d1042b40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國會於去年11月通過《香港人權與民主法案》（下稱《法案》）．網媒HKFP調查發現，港府在2014至2020年期間，透過香港貿易發展局，向美國的游說公司支付至少8,400萬港元，聘用包括前美國國會議員的說客進行「政治活動」，及安排與美國政客會面。商經局發言人向HKFP表示，政府在華盛頓的代表當時積極解釋香港的情況，並對《法案》提出強烈反對。翻查資料，《法案》於19年獲參議院一致通過，眾議院則以417票贊成、1票反對壓倒性通過。換言之，政府豪花近億公帑，僅「成功」換到一票。<br />\n<br />\n商經局晚上回覆《蘋果》時，沒有正面回應上述支出問題，僅稱香港駐美國的經濟貿易辦事處一直與美國各界保持恆常聯繫，就《法案》而言，香港駐華盛頓經貿辦一直透過不同渠道向有關人士和機構解說香港的情況，「積極澄清部份人士的誤解及糾正錯誤報告，尤其對於一些誤解和不實的情況」。"},{"pid":"a3d2109081a6ed904d9132ad760c9b6cd36d1555","tid":2495992,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ba80b2ac676f68417cb707298c4f92925478d","tid":2495992,"uid":100772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"即刻個1票收哂錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dffea9086066bb855bc80554b908547e9c64549","tid":2495992,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:47:13.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />